PrecisRe-appointment of SUPARNA GHOSH, of Toronto, Ontario, CLIVE JOAKIM, of Markham, Ontario, DIANE C. SMITH, of Toronto, Ontario, SYLVIA ROY, of Thunder Bay, Ontario, and NINA STANWICK, of North York, Ontario, as full-time members of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years, effective January 20, 2000.
